.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt bdmenu 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm bdmenu
.Nd an application launcher like
.Xr dmenu_run 1
with recent input management
and possibility to open in a terminal.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
shows a list of commands that can be executed with, in
first, the most recently opened.

If the chosen entry ends with a "!", the command is opened
in a terminal.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr dmenu 1
.Xr term 1
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal
	top! : open "top" in a terminal
	firefox : open firefox
.Ed
